Ɔbenfo Aba. A. Bentil Andam yɛ Ghana ni abɔdeɛ mu nyansapɛ ne fa ɛhwɛ mfidi dwuma ne ahoɔden kunini.  Yɛwoo no wɔ afe apem ahankorɔn aduonan nwɔtwe (1948) mu. Ɔbɛyɛɛ panin a ɔda kuo ah ɛhwɛ abɔdeɛ mu nyansapɛ sua soɔ wɔ Ghana mu wɔ 2017-2019. Ɔno ne Ghana nii ɔbaa ah odii kan nyaa abɔdin wɔ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ sua ne fa ɛhwɛ mfidi dwuma ne ahoɔdenneɛ mu.<ref>https://www.ghanabusinessnews.com/2016/03/12/ghanas-first-female-physicist-calls-for-gender-parity-in-science/</ref>

== Abrabɔ nne nteteɛ ==
Yɛwoo Aba afe 1948 mu wɔ Adwumako kɔkɔben wɔ ɔman Ghana mu. Ɔkɔɔ ne ntoasoɔ sukuu wɔ Mfantseman sukuupɔn (Mfantseman Girls SHS). Na ɔkɔɔ Oguaa sukuupɔn (UCC) wɔ afe 1969 na owiee n'adesua 1973, Ɛhɔ na ɔnyaa n'abɔdin krataa wɔ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ ne fǎ a ɛhwɛ mfididwuma ne ahoɔden ɛne nkotaabuo mu. Ɔkɔ toaa n'adesua so wɔ Birmingham suapɔn mu (University of Birmingham) wɔ afe 1976-1977 mu, ɛna Durham Suapɔn (Durham University) wɔ afe 1978-1981. Bere a na ɔwɔ Oguaa suapɔn ne Durham suapɔn mu no, na ɔno ne ɔbaa baakopɛ aa na ɔregye adesua nteteɛ wɔ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ ne fǎ a ɛhwɛ mfididwuma ne ahoɔden sua ho.

== Ne Nwomasua ne Abrabɔ ==
Aba Bentil bɛyɛɛ abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ fa a ɛhwɛ mfididwuma ne ahoɔden kuo ba wɔ afe 1986 mu.  Ɛsiane n'anigye ɛwɔ nwomasua mu nti, ɔwɔ abɔdin nkrataa ahoroɔ wɔ French kasa sua ne n'atwerɛ mu.  Ebi ne:  <nowiki>''</nowiki>Diplome de Langue d’Alliance Francaise de Paris; the French Proficiency Certificate of Ghana Institute of Languages; and the Certificate of Translation, Alliance Francaise de Paris.<nowiki>''</nowiki>

Ɛwɔ afe 1986 & 1987 mu no Aba kɔsuaa adeɛ wɔ Germany man mu ( research station DESY;Deutsches Elektronen-Synchrotron).  Ɔhyɛɛ aseɛ yɛɛ nhwehwɛmu ɛfaa kwan ah ahoɔden nframa efiri mfidie ahoroɔ ha nnipa ne kwan a yɛbɛtumi asi ano.  Ɛwɔ afe 1987 ahyɛseɛ mu no, ɔyɛɛ amerado maa kuo a na ɛhyɛ mmaa nkumaa nkuran sɛ wɔn so bɛtumi asua abɔdeɛmu nyansapɛ na w'abɛyɛ emu akunini.
